data.description: This luxurious Duplex is in the Medical Distract (JPS, Baylor, Harries, Medical City) near TCU, Downtown Fort Worth, highways 35W, 30, and highway 20. It is also close to EM Daggett Elementary, Daggett Middle School and Paschal High School, near the Historic Fairmount District. It would be great for Doctors, Nurse, Medical Students.  Stainless Steel Appliances, Granite Counter Tops, Alarm System, Ceramic Tile flooring in Kitchen, Bathrooms, and Laundry, Real WOOD Floors throughout, Full fenced back yard great for small dogs.
